            <a href="https://s.id/pesertaroadshowhoki" class="py-4 px-8 rounded-xl bg-secondary text-tertiary w-fit font-semibold my-4">Daftar Roadshow</a>

            <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-tertiary">Keuntungan Mengikuti Campus Roadshow HoKi</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
