          </div>
          <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h3 class="flex md:hidden text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 w-full mt-6">4 Februari - 15 April 2023</h3>
            <div class="flex p-5 rounded-xl shadow-md text-tertiary font-semibold w-full max-w-sm border">Pendampingan Bisnis 10 Finalis (Hybrid)</div>
